Acceptance: Verify Bot Connector OpenID metadata/JWKS and RS256 signature, issuer, audience, time claims, tenant, activity serviceUrl against its token claim, and channel/key endorsements when supplied; cache keys with rotation/refetch and fail closed on fetch, key, claim, tenant, or provenance failure. Only immutable tenant plus Teams user ID forms the canonical human identity; bots and mutable display fields cannot. Canonical contract: docs/plans/2026-07-13-github-user-attribution-and-feature-discovery.md.